  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4\u0da2\u0db1 \u0d8b\u0db4\u0dba\u0ddd\u0d9c\u0dd3\u0dad\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0db8\u0dda \u0dc3\u0db7\u0dcf\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d89\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The Chairman of the Public Utilities Commission is requested to be removed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "At the ruling party meeting held yesterday (04), a group of MPs have requested that the chairman of the Public Utilities Commission, Mr. Janaka Ratnayake, be removed from that position.",
        "The MPs have pointed out that the government is also embarrassed by the misleading statements made by the Chairman of the Public Utility Commission at the press conference.",
        "Therefore, the MPs have requested the President and the Prime Minister to take steps to remove him immediately",
        "Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe who has replied to this has stated that if he hands over a letter signed by 113 Members of Parliament, steps can be taken to remove him."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "the Public Utilities Commission",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
